    "longBusinessSummary": "ACC Binh Duong Investment and Construction Joint Stock Company manufactures and supplies products and materials for the construction of transportation, civil, industrial, public works, and technical infrastructure applications in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers hot asphalt concrete, cement concrete carpets, road marking paints construction services, precast concrete structural products, reinforced concrete sewer manufacturing products and concrete structures, and prefabricated structures. It also involved transportation of raw materials and products, and construction projects. In addition, the company engages in the real estate business, such as ownership, use rights, and rental of land; rental of machinery, equipment, and other tangible goods; wholesales of certain goods; and cutting, shaping, and finishing of stone business. The company was formerly known as Becamex Asphalt & Concrete Joint Stock Company and changed its name to ACC Binh Duong Investment and Construction Joint Stock Company in May 2019. ACC Binh Duong Investment and Construction Joint Stock Company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Ben Cát, Vietnam.",
